column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec, dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type, f.psfWidth_r FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoObjAll p ON p.objID = x.objID JOIN Field f ON f.field = p.field WHERE (((p.psfMag_r - p.modelMag_r) < # AND p.psfMag_r < #) OR (p.parentID = #)) AND p.probPSF = # ORDER BY x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
